commit.message: Small correction to readme.

Updated readme with more examples.
Now using update_centroids_from_list function in from_dict.
Added iter function so you can iterate over the centroids.
Updated readme with new to_dict and update_from_dict methods.
Added tests for new to_dict and update methods.

Added lots of examples to docstring, new method names for to_dict and update_from_dict.
Removed n value because it should be computed from centroid counts.
Values for delta and K are now optional.
Created similar methods for people who might want to update from/get a list of centroid values.
Added serialize and deserialize methods
